      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, roadworthy condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a budget-friendly commuter. The engine and transmission are fully functional and have been regularly serviced to ensure reliable daily use. However, the exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows typical wear on the upholstery and some minor cosmetic blemishes on the dashboard. It\u2019s a solid choice for a buyer looking for a reliable runner who doesn't mind a bit of character and cosmetic work.",
