    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exquisite example of automotive excellence, this vehicle arrives in impeccable, showroom-condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standards, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to absolute quality. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive statement in mechanical and aesthetic perfection, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut.",
      "price": 48500.0,
