    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's honestly in incredible shape. I've taken such good care of it that it still feels like it just left the dealership! It's been garage-kept, meticulously maintained, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
