      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a superlative example of the E46 M3, a hallmark of analog performance. This S54-powered coupe features a meticulously maintained 3.2L inline-six, with documented rod bearing replacement and a fully bulletproofed Double VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gates, sending power to the rear wheels via a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term structural durability. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. The exterior retains its deep luster with no evidence of panel fatigue or paint degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and high-revving atmospheric induction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
