    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom masterpiece, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-luster finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip, while the interior remains in factory-fresh condition, retaining that distinct new-car scent. Every surface, from the supple, uncreased leather upholstery to the polished interior trim, is immaculate. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, backed by a comprehensive and fully documented service history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a turn-key example that requires absolutely zero compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
